{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":60,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mo_xi","speaker_name":"莫西","listener":null,"text":"我姓莫的招子不亮，不知道朋友是高人，今天认栽了，朋友念在同是武林一脉，亮个万儿，青山不改，绿水长流，山不转路转，以后见着面，我姓莫的兄弟七人，总有补报朋友之处。","tone":"陈述","chapter":5,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_mo_xi","speaker_name":"莫西","listener":"char_ai_qing","text":"朋友，你未免也太不讲江湖道理了，我姓莫的连毛都没有碰着你的，你又何必苦苦相逼。","tone":"颤声","chapter":5,"line_start":24,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_mo_xi","speaker_name":"莫西","listener":null,"text":"朋友你看看该怎么办就怎么办吧！","tone":"无奈","chapter":5,"line_start":30,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_mo_xi","speaker_name":"莫西","listener":null,"text":"千手书生！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":5,"line_start":40,"line_end":41},{"speaker":"char_ai_qing","speaker_name":"艾青","listener":null,"text":"千手书生！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":5,"line_start":40,"line_end":40}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ai_qing","name":"艾青","alias":["冷月仙子"],"identity":"冷月仙子，千手书生之妻","faction":null,"role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":7,"one_line":"冷月仙子，武功高强，杀伐果断的女魔头","personality":{"traits":["冷酷","果断","高傲","杀伐决断","软硬不吃","美丽"],"speech_style":"冷然","temperament":"冷酷"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_mo_xi","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"追杀"},{"target":"char_pei_jue","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"暂时同行"}],"known_skills":["skill_wan_liu_gui_zong"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[5],"source_refs":[{"chapter":5,"line_start":1,"line_end":60,"text":"冷月仙子追杀莫西"}]},{"id":"char_mo_xi","name":"莫西","alias":["三煞","北斗七煞三煞"],"identity":"北斗七煞中的三煞","faction":null,"role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":4,"one_line":"北斗七煞三煞，擅长七星神弩暗器，被冷月仙子追杀","personality":{"traits":["老江湖","色厉内荏","经验丰富","阴险","好色"],"speech_style":"老江湖口吻","temperament":"暴躁"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ai_qing","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"被追杀"}],"known_skills":["skill_wu_hu_duan_men_dao","skill_qi_xing_shen_nu"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[5],"source_refs":[{"chapter":5,"line_start"